# VQE Molecular Benchmarks

Reproducible benchmarks for Variational Quantum Eigensolver (VQE) across 
three qubit mappings (Jordan-Wigner, Bravyi-Kitaev, Parity) and three 
molecules (H₂, LiH, N₂).

## Reproduce Everything in 3 Commands

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/vqe-molecular-benchmarks
cd vqe-molecular-benchmarks
pip install -r requirements.txt && python run_all.py
```

